transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Hello, Pawan ji baat kar rahe hai na sir?
Customer: Haan ji, haan ji.
Executive: Haan ji, haan ji. Ashrita, good evening IndiaMART se aapne call kiya tha na ek baar 96 customer care pe.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Haan ji, toh aapke uske baad aapki phir account manager se baat bhi ho gayi hogi. Toh uske liye aapke WhatsApp pe ek message aaya hoga IndiaMART ki taraf se, ek baar check kariye.

Customer: Nahi aaya abhi tak.
Executive: IndiaMART ki taraf se aaya hoga message.
Customer: Are nahi aaya na. Aata toh mai aapko bata deta.
summary:
